org.peertrust.parser.prolog
Class PrologGrammarTokenManager

java.lang.Object
  org.peertrust.parser.prolog.PrologGrammarTokenManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
PrologGrammarConstants
public class PrologGrammarTokenManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrologGrammarConstants

This class represents Prolog parser. It consists of three methods ConvertRules() and SyntaxCheck() to be used for converting Prolog programs to PeerTrust and automatically generated methods for parsing.
